docs {
  ## Create Experiment - Image (V1)

  Creates an Image generation experiment. Models are string arrays (e.g. "256-x-256/dall-e-2").
  model_params include `n` (number of images) and `dropdowns.size`.
  output_format is "image".
  This example shows multiple prompt_config entries.

  ### Response
  ```json
  {"message": "Experiment created successfully.", "status": 200}
  ```
}
